          "question": "<p><a name=\"2235\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Given \\( \\Sigma=\\{a,b\\} \\), which one of the following sets is not countable?</p>\n\n</div><br><br><b>GATE CSE 1997 | Question: 3.4</b></p>",
