            "<p>\\( 2^{\\Sigma^*} \\) is uncountable and \\( \\Sigma^* \\) is countable</p>",
            "<p>Both \\( 2^{\\Sigma^*} \\) and \\( \\Sigma^* \\) are uncountable</p>"
